=== LIGHT_BRIDGE_PUZZLE ===
# id: 54
# title: The Light Bridge
# chinese_title: 光桥之谜
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

A chasm splits the corridor, far too wide to jump. On both sides, crystal prisms are mounted on adjustable pedestals. A beam of light enters from a small window. If you can align the prisms correctly, the refracted light should activate the hard-light bridge generator.

* [Carefully align the prisms]
  ~ gain_radical("光")
  "光" (guāng) — light, ray, brightness
* [Calculate the optimal angles first]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "算" (suàn) — to calculate, to figure out
* [Use your own light source to cheat]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "巧" (qiǎo) — clever, skillful
* [Find another way across]
  ~ nothing
  "桥" (qiáo) — bridge
